{
  "stem": "294.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the meantime, the Germans came, a few of them, and they started to beat the girls horribly, because they went outside, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a terrible time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We also had to all wash in the latrines, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everything was better than we-- we had afterwards, in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was from horrible as comparing--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to our regular life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no-- only for women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Men and-- or women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some men did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mostly not men and not husbands and wives-- [LAUGHS] --but, you know, boyfriends, girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes it happens, but this was severely punished too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A man could have been shot like if he will be caught.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hanging, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hanging, yes, and I also saw people shot--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because this was an instance when a few prisoners tried to escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in order to teach the rest of the prisoners a lesson, they arranged for all of us to stay on the appellplatz, which was a roll-call square, and witness the execution.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were hanged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the whole-- the whole camp had to be there and witness this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On another occasion, the Germans killed the-- the Polish-- the Jewish Police commandant-- the one I mentioned before-- his assistant, the commandant's wife, and a few other people, connected with the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were-- I didn't see the shooting, but I saw them dead, laying on the ground.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the whole camp had to pass by them and look at them.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
